title: Why Microsoft Stock Topped the Market Today
description: A smart push into artificial intelligence (AI) was benefiting Microsoft (NASDAQ: MSFT) and its shareholders on Wednesday.  A business the tech company has placed a bet on announced a move aimed at capitalizing on its famous innovation, and investors were guardedly optimistic about that development.  OpenAI, the platform's developer, announced on its official blog that it's launching a pilot subscription plan called ChatGPT plus.

title: Powell poprawił nastroje na Wall Street
description: S&P500 zyskał w środę 1,0 proc., a Nasdaq Composite poszedł w górę o 2,0 proc. Średnia Przemysłowa Dow Jones rosła na zamknięciu o mniej niż 0,1 proc.
